Comment: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:02.63,songtitle,,0,0,0,,「灯火のまにまに」 作詞、編曲：ZAI-ON，作曲：WEST GROUND，主唱：東山奈央
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:05.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,そっと心の奥　光宿した
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:09.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,灯火のまにまに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:23.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,立ち込める八重霞　彷徨い歩き
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:27.95,OPJP,,0,0,0,,淡き夢から覚め
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:35.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,ひとすじ頬伝った涙の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:41.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,滲んだ世界を彩る影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:54.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,夜の帳　揺れる鬼火　遠い日の記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:01:00.08,OPJP,,0,0,0,,隠世へ誘え
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:03.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,ゆらり　ゆらり　舞い散る桜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:06.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,心を薄紅に染めゆく想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:12.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,あなたの横顔　月夜が照らし出す 見上げれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:15.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,きらり　きらり　願いの欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:18.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,幾千の星の様に煌めいて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:27.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,心の宵闇に朝日が昇るよう 灯火のまにまに
Comment: 0,0:00:00.07,0:00:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:05.17,OPCH,,0,0,0,,光悄悄在心中萌芽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.43,0:00:09.70,OPCH,,0,0,0,,任憑燈火所指引
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:23.54,OPCH,,0,0,0,,誤入層層迷霧之中 徘徊漫步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.99,0:00:27.95,OPCH,,0,0,0,,從虛幻的夢醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.38,0:00:35.51,OPCH,,0,0,0,,一道道殘留在臉頰的淚痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:41.64,OPCH,,0,0,0,,影子為模糊的世界色彩上了顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:54.09,OPCH,,0,0,0,,夜幕中 搖曳的鬼火 往昔的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.34,0:01:00.08,OPCH,,0,0,0,,正邀請我前往隱世
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.36,0:01:03.23,OPCH,,0,0,0,,搖曳吧 搖曳吧 散落舞動的櫻花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:06.52,OPCH,,0,0,0,,使心頭染上緋紅的想念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.74,0:01:12.39,OPCH,,0,0,0,,你的側臉 被月夜照映了出來 彷彿昂首可見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:15.40,OPCH,,0,0,0,,閃爍的 閃爍的 願望的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.42,0:01:18.36,OPCH,,0,0,0,,像是繁星一般閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:27.99,OPCH,,0,0,0,,心中的暗夜也升起了朝陽 任憑燈火所指引
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:32.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天神屋就這麼讓客人在前廳枯等的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折尾屋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.20,0:01:39.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貿然到訪錯在我方 給掌櫃的添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.67,0:01:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊 曉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都當上掌櫃了 真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:54.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你離開天神屋時指名要我繼任的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:56.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請稍待片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.55,0:01:59.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見 銀次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折尾屋的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.19,0:02:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是銀次先生的熟人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 銀次先生以前在折尾屋工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 今天客房已經客滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得想來天神屋住一晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽鳥 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正值旺季 應該要提前預約的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實在是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不覺得有點過於冷淡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.47,0:02:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把房間讓出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.64,0:02:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡夕顏就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉和料理也都享用過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐 這樣太...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 信前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟這位親切的小姐打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.19,0:02:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,銀次 看你這麼有精神真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:01.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是沒看到大老闆出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:02.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他出門了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個浴場管理員...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴場管理員？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽鳥我先去泡溫泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是來者不善啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天狗羽鳥先生是折尾屋的掌櫃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時彥先生是負責管理浴場事務的一把手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 幹活啦 幹活啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的崗位在夕顏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在夕顏做好力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有信件 有信件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是大老闆大人給我的通信木板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到現世了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說妳把房間讓給了折尾屋的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信件來得正是時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在夕顏做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:26.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼想要的禮物的話儘管開口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禮物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...我想想看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？靜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很為難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很為難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...那個客人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要插嘴 人類的小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是來接靜奈的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…但...但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 靜奈我...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時彥大人被稱作不知火 是妖火中最高位的大妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是養育我的親人 也是我的師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅？教妳管理浴場的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時彥大人希望我能回到折尾屋...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到他的身邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈 要回折尾屋了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.85,0:05:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我要留在天神屋工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天神屋對我有收留之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.52,0:05:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且現在我也有徒弟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是和音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是曾經的師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然就要妳回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈妳當然會不樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...不樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實 師傅表達愛意的方式是有點過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護過度 認真過頭 絮絮叨叨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容易誤會 還容易受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 是他內心陰暗又相當麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這樣我也一直...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不..不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.48,0:06:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出生在南之地的貧困山區
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個一無是處的濡女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被時彥大人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將我帶回折尾屋 細心又嚴格地養育我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和時彥大人的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,改變了我的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了不輸給擁有隱世第一溫泉的天神屋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,折尾屋斥重金尋找溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一心想著幫助師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四處探尋溫泉之源
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一天 找到了一個小小的泉眼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是可以隨意觸碰的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:01.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人為了保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受了無法癒合的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個火焰就是力量從傷口洩漏形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給折尾屋帶來了沉重的損失 被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人到最後一刻都還在為我爭取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我無法原諒自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:48.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我就被大老闆大人撿了回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:08:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久沒吃到剛出爐的飯菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 這個謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮的髮帶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是師傅大人第一次買給我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修業時 師傅大人都是用這髮帶給我綁頭髮的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈明明這麼仰慕時彥先生 為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個...大概是因為我還不夠自信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.91,0:08:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我自己滿意為止 都要在這裡好好努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.50,0:08:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大老闆大人說過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多熟客 是因為喜歡靜奈調製的溫泉才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很認可靜奈的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.88,0:08:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點讓人羨襄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.93,0:08:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個叫做「冰沙」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅茄子？隱世是這麼叫番茄的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人很喜歡種菜 特別是種紅茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就連討厭蔬菜的我 在一起做飯的過程中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也慢慢喜歡上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈 找到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有緊急的幹部會議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是關於折尾屋那幫人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺心情舒暢多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 少女心真是難懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時彥先生一定是誤以為被靜奈小姐拒絕了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他看起來有點消瘦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是因為那傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧？ 臉色很難看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.39,0:10:18.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的 讓妳擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼是我能為靜奈和時彥先生做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇…嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}有信件 有信件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想好要什麼禮物了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大老闆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起禮物 能幫我跑個腿嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說在現世跑腿 也是丈夫的一項任務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.72,0:11:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要什麼牌子的巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做原料用的 大袋裝的就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有酵母 泡打粉 小麥粉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:12.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待小葵做的麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在得到大老闆大人的幾分認可了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:20.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為天神屋的一員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他對我抱有期待嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.83,0:11:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有天神屋的大家就拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我會努力跑腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 大老闆大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就只有做菜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈和她師傅好像都喜歡西紅柿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個說不定能派上什麼用場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是折尾屋的..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.62,0:12:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信前輩 你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是吃了您要賣的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 這只是試作品 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下定決心要在這裡努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哩？發生什麼事了 葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那隻狗是折尾屋的幹部嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是受大家喜歡的招牌狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從創立起就擔任宣傳部長的重量級人物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,員工們都尊稱它為「信前輩」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很樸實的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在現世很流行用豆渣做點心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說是低熱量有助健康
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信前輩可能是被這香味吸引來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳是在擔心什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？沒...沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要在走廊上奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕〜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是沒變啊 曉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:33.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.92,0:13:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說 我沒辦法回到師傅的身邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:53.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我恐怕 徹底地被她討厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定覺得我性格陰沉還糾纏不清
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我能理解您的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是靜奈離開折尾屋的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留給我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已經不會回到我身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以必須把這個還給她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳看起來和靜奈關係不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就麻煩妳幫我交給她了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好...好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎..怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐 冰沙還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊嘞嘞 這個髮帶不是還給靜奈了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個啊 是另外一條
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說是一對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果把這個交給靜奈的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們倆就真的...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.30,0:15:05.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占用妳一點時間可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點東西想跟妳分享
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是番茄醬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼醬？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊〜番茄的香味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:24.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚐嚐看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:28.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨時都能嚐到番茄味道的調味料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多好的東西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:37.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多料理裡都能用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了很多所以分妳一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個如果可以的話 下次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請教我做會用到番茄醬的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳很喜歡番茄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯〜非常喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為能讓妳想起師傅嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次和女性朋友一起做料理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因為我沒什麼朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也嚐一下番茄醬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:14.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很配秋葵肉卷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜品是番茄冰沙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 銀次先生還在折尾屋的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道靜奈和時彥的事情了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是跟他們也不是很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈其實很想儘快回到他的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是她回不去折尾屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為讓師傅受傷了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈也很後悔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時彥也早就原諒她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她被折尾屋解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這已經不是他們兩個人之間的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於認真又重情重義的她來說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離開對她有收留之恩的天神屋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕是也做不到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話 靜奈該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 她現在正盡可能地回避她師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實如銀次所說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:29.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 我也不能就這樣袖手旁觀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然知道了他們倆的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 如果可以的話 今晚的晚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能來夕顏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想大家或許想吃一頓輕鬆的晚宴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙對吃的一點都不感興趣 很無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前可不是這樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羽鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,番茄料理怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,番茄 我倒是很喜歡番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:13.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要還給靜奈的話 請自己交還
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在夕顏恭候您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.99,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要逃避 把你的真實想法當面 告訴時彥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒自信什麼的 天神屋什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都不用考慮 把妳的心願都說出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心願...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是番茄宴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈來幫忙了 準備工作比想像的完成得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵小姐教了我很多番茄料理的做法 我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我打算用烏龍麵做那不勒斯義大利麵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:18:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用烏龍麵？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是既沒有香腸也沒有培根啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用肉沫做肉丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.54,0:19:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是加了肉丸的那不勒斯烏龍麵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.33,0:19:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能幫上什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:12.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈的話 麻煩妳準備肉丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和時彥先生一起做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師...師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和師傅一起做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一會兒大家都會來吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以需要很多肉丸子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽羽鳥先生說時彥先生 最近對吃的沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...想和師傅一起做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時彥先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈估計需要用一下髮帶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.16,0:20:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做料理的話 要把頭髮綁起來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 好了 兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快洗洗手 開工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這些原料全部做成丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:20:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後放到鐵板上烤哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美〜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅 一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.60,0:21:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是第一次吃 卻不可思議的覺得這個味道很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天 我會成為能幫上忙的靜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到師傅的身邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳已經有了自己的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就為了自己而奮鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:55.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個小姑娘 還真有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.05,0:22:00.04,title,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}溫泉師濡女與師傅不知火
Comment: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:03.53,songtitle,,0,0,0,,「彩 -color-」 作詞、主唱：沼倉愛美，作曲：WEST GROUND，編曲：ZAI-ON
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:04.49,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}ふわふわ浮かぶ白い心が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:11.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}あたためられてそっと 目覚める
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:20.53,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}やがて 舞い降 りていく  何もない場所でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:25.83,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}風が 薫って  声こえ がとどいた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.83,0:22:32.57,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}守られてること 気づかなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:36.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}あんなに 近くにいたころには
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.76,0:22:40.85,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}彩られてく 心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.16,0:22:49.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}もうひとつの世界 旅立とう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:53.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}願いが 繋ぐ 私の物語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:57.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}この手がつくりだす笑顔たち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:04.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}今が軌跡に変わっていく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:08.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}終わらない終わらない虹の先
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:12.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}そう  誰かのために生きること
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:19.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}出会えたの まぶしい未来と
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:04.49,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}潔白的心 輕飄飄地浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.79,0:22:11.56,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}被溫暖著 不知不覺醒了過來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:20.53,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}雪開始飄然落下 在這什麼都沒有的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.09,0:22:25.83,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}有芬芳的風和傳達心意的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.83,0:22:32.57,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}我沒有意識到我一直被守護著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:36.73,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}直到你離我那麼近的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.76,0:22:40.85,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}變得越來越多彩的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.16,0:22:49.18,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}在已經是兩人共同的世界中 啟程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:53.74,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}願望維繫著我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:57.76,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}這雙手創造的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.27,0:23:04.74,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}現在逐漸變成了過去的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:08.08,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}不會結束 不會結束 在彩虹的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.22,0:23:12.06,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}為了誰而活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:19.63,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fad(200,200)}能與你相遇的絢爛的未來
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濡女他們和好如初了 真是大好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這次天狗們又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,槽了 夕顏要被毀了
